{"tid":2057051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中華白海豚屍體南丫島水域擱淺 本年度第23宗","createTime":"2020-06-09T06:23:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T06:34:05.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2e4c73f03be9e75564cf1832c77c5e52f6584f9d","tid":2057051,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:23:08.000Z","msg":"中華白海豚屍體南丫島水域擱淺 本年度第23宗<br />\n2020-06-09 HKT 13:11<br />\n<br />\n一條中華白海豚屍體被發現在南丫島水域擱淺，是本年度的第23宗，這條雌性年幼海豚身長約115厘米，已被送往海洋公園作詳細解剖。 <br />\n<br />\n海洋公園保育基金表示，昨午接報通知，發現海豚屍體已嚴重腐爛。基金呼籲公眾若發現懷疑鯨豚擱淺，可致電1823熱線，並提供發現擱淺的時間、地點或相片，以便行動組盡快到場跟進。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531021-20200609.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531021-20200609.htm&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7Xelv5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=11e1238a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1531021-20200609.htm&h=9297d4b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1531021-20200609.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3eddc1848ee8c2b4f86e72d03c3613ca8277693c","tid":2057051,"uid":156144,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"咁死法10年會唔會絕種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce1bbaca6cce790e9a40089fa81eb4de73bcc9d5","tid":2057051,"uid":243075,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:25:12.000Z","msg":"手足RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3ae29f646f872d8abfa038b9b479368328e7cc","tid":2057051,"uid":189986,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老母大白象公程"},{"pid":"177078c1004771bbfa580786efed83aa6f4